(Yes, Inferno, I have control of the Newcomer characters of mine now)

Koga Shuko/Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:



Koga Shuko looked to the bounty hunters in his ship.  "No, I have no need for 
you right now.  Go ahead and seek other jobs."

===

Imprisoner looked to Hot Rod, who was following him.  Taking out his missile 
launcher from subspace, he pointed it near Hot Rod.  "Continuation of your 
following us, will be taken as an act of hostilities." 
The three Predacons continued on their way.
